ch Themes】Disaster, folk horror, adventure, mystery......Multiple themed scripts can be played anytime, anywhere, with an immersive experience.<br>【Strong Randomness】Each adventure introduces random scenes, encounters, and deduction plots, providing stronger replayability. Hidden items and clues lead to unexpected truths, which requires you to explore and win by unexpected means.<br>【Multiple Endings】Each script has more than 5 endings, your choice determines the plot direction, and the story is written by you.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2168810/extras/d7301b59cd46906a6f30a42692826356.poster.avif?t=1705297849\" width=628 height=352 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2168810/extras/d7301b59cd46906a6f30a42692826356.webm?t=1705297849\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2168810/extras/d7301b59cd46906a6f30a42692826356.mp4?t=1705297849\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Dice Rolling</h2>Roll the dice to determine your fate! Inheriting the essence of TRPG, the game's development is determined by random dice rolls. Will you win in danger or have an unexpected accident? Be kind to your dice, and your dice will be kind to you!<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2168810/extras/acded24f573361f645f7c5784927b2f1.poster.avif?t=1705297849\" width=628 height=352 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2168810/extras/acded24f573361f645f7c5784927b2f1.webm?t=1705297849\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2168810/extras/acded24f573361f645f7c5784927b2f1.mp4?t=170529